item.title: Adulting
item.description: Last year I became a member of a club that no one wants to talk about. A club in which membership is one of the most painful experiences most will face in their lifetime and all are pretty much powerless to avoid. We found out we were expecting a baby in December 2017, excited and full of hope and expectation we celebrated. As tradition encourages we were hoping to share our good news after the first scan at 12 weeksâ€¦.
